A woman makes "simit", a kind of Turkish traditional circular bread, in Malatya province, Turkey, on July 15, 2019. The simit is one of the most popular breakfast in Turkey. Residents of Malatya have a long history of using traditional tandoors to make simits. (Xinhua)  

